snippet.title: Hal Life 1 - Official GameSpot trailer / High Quality, Stereo
snippet.description:
GameSpot Half Life Trailer [1998 trailer]
This trailer was made 1 month after Half Life 1 was launched. Its very old so theres no better quality.
